# Scenario: User Cannot Sign In

## Issue
User reports “invalid credentials” when signing in.

## Possible Causes
- Incorrect password
- Account locked
- MFA failure
- Sign-in blocked by policy

## Troubleshooting Steps
1. Check sign-in logs in Entra ID
2. Confirm account status (enabled/disabled)
3. Reset password if needed
4. Verify MFA configuration

## Resolution
Restore access by resetting credentials and verifying account status.
